# Repository-specific ARCH rule extensions preserved across upgrade.
# Base file: .orch/rules/app/arch.rules
app/internal/service|app/internal/infra|service must not depend on concrete infra
app/internal/service|app/internal/config|service must not depend on config
app/internal/service|app/internal/runtime|service must not depend on runtime packages
app/internal/transport/httpapi/drain|app/internal/runtime|http drain must not depend on runtime
app/internal/transport/httpapi/metrics|app/internal/runtime|http metrics must not depend on runtime
